Name.subject: Bunche, Ralph J. (Ralph Johnson), $d 1904-1971
Author: Bunche, Ralph, Jr.
Name.repository: University of California, Los Angeles. Library. Department of Special Collections
Description.note: Certificate presented to Ralph J. Bunche upon receiving the Nobel Peace Prize by his son Ralph Bunche, Jr. Certificate created by a professional calligrapher (signed, Anthony '50) with modern day decorations including initial foliate "D" along the left-hand side and pastel colored pebbles along the bottom|~|Digitization took place as part of the California Cultures Project.|~|"Dear Daddy, I am happy you got the Nobel Peace Prize. Love, Ralph"
Title: Congratulatory certificate, from Ralph Bunche, Jr. to his father, Ralph J. Bunche.
